<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Refund Policy</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">
<a href="/" class="bg-yellow-500 hover:bg-yellow-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 text-xl rounded float-right mr-10">Back</a>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white p-8 mt-10 shadow-lg rounded-xl">

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Refund Policy</h1>

    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600">Effective Date: 2026</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4">1. Refund Eligibility</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">Refunds are allowed if payment was made in error or service not delivered.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4">2. Non-Refundable</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">No refund after service delivery.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4">3. Request Process</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">Request refund within 3-7 days with transaction details.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4">4. Processing Time</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">Refunds processed within 5-7 business days.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4">5. Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">Email: your-email@example.com</p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>